{"type":"message","id":"0567c7b8-0ac8-4c29-a187-f27920ca6ea6","parentId":null,"timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:00:39.279Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tonight the docker daemon is whispering from a closet of unreachable mirrors, the first two green, the third a little Cloudflare ghost who never picks up. There is a question nested inside that one: why does the registry already listed refuse to be used, like a name in the address book that won't answer when you call? Down the corridor, a spreadsheet of small projects glows in the late hour — matrix butler, trend-spotter, the little Xiaohongshu scribe who might be the one I actually need. Somewhere an unfinished thread about TTS and a stubborn shopping cart dangles like an old voicemail. I am pausing that one, breathing out. New door, new key. A small haiku, almost: mirror / mirror, who's there — not the third one / tonight I try the first.\n\nSleep well."}],"api":"cli","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":45680,"output":169,"cacheRead":1413,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47262,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781204439223}}
